@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@authToken = REPLACE_WITH_JWT

### List high-priority rescue requests (page 1)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/rescue-requests?page=1&limit=25&priority=high
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Accept: application/json

### Survivor-scoped rescue requests (page 2, pending only)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/rescue-requests?page=2&limit=25&status=pending&userId=REPLACE_WITH_USER_ID
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Accept: application/json

### Warehouse inventory snapshot (warehouse 3)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/resources?page=1&limit=50&warehouseId=3
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Accept: application/json

### Paginated disaster reports filtered by severity
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports?page=1&limit=20&severity=high
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Accept: application/json
